kdna-react provides React components and hooks for building
KDNA-integrated web applications. Components handle file selection,
load-plan state, password entry, license activation, asset inspection,
and server-mediated asset loading.

This package calls a compatible KDNA server endpoint from React
components and hooks. Decryption and license verification are always
delegated to a server running @aikdna/kdna-web-server.

